%^CYAN%^BOLD%^EGOIST%^RESET%^

The egoist is a psion who specializes in altering their own bodies to achieve results
well beyond what a normal person can achieve. Egoists can be excellent fighters and
excel at close combat.

%^BOLD%^Egoist Feats:%^RESET%^

L2 : metabolic healing
L11: resilient body
L21: infused form

%^BOLD%^Egosit Spells:%^RESET%^

thicken skin
animal affinity
chameleon
deathward
breath of life
restoration
rewind age
lesser transformation
shadow double
shadow body

See Also: disciplines, telepath, nomad, seer, shaper, kineticist